<p>
<lb n="1"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> <unclear>vi</unclear>gege <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> mūvattaAṟa suṁka<note n="372-1">The beginning of the record is lost.</note>
<lb n="2"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> māḍi caṁdrādityaruḷḷannakaraṁ koṭṭaru svadattāṁ
<lb n="3"/>paradattāṁ vā yō harēta vasuṁdharā <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> ṣṭāyāṁ jāyatē krimi matta(ṁ)mā tatpu
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṇyadinadalu bāḍada <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> <unclear>yī</unclear>śvaradēvargge caitrada parvvakke bēḷe pavitrada parvvakke bē
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ḷeya biṭṭaru <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> mattaṁ śrīmadaśēsamahā <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> kāḍa vūroḍeyaru bāḍada vūruṁba
<lb n="6"/>hokharaṇeyiṁdaṁ baḍagalu śrī kēśavadēvarggaveṁdu bhaṁḍi bhattada keya dhārāpūrvvakaṁ māḍi
<lb n="7"/>sarvvanamasyavāgi koṭṭaru
</p>

